# Agent pipeline runtime files (change every run — not version controlled)
.agents/feedback.md
.agents/test-tasks.md
.agents/execution-log.md

# Heal-gate baselines: the Generate stage snapshots each freshly-generated spec here so the
# over-heal gate can diff a same-run heal against the pre-heal version. Per-run scratch, not committed.
.agents/heal-baseline/

# Pipeline scratch artifacts (binary / per-cycle debug output — cleared at cycle start)
.playwright-mcp/
/*.png
/*.jpe?g

# NOTE: .agents/archive/ and .agents/pipeline-status.md are intentionally NOT ignored —
# archive/ is the durable QA trail, pipeline-status.md is the at-a-glance current state.

# --- Maintainer's local showcase demos (kept local, never pushed) ---
# This repo is a clean, forkable template: the remote ships only tests/_shared/ (the
# infra every target needs) and empty per-target structure. The demos below are used
# locally to showcase the pipeline against real sites — ignored so a stray `git add .`
# can't push them into the template. They are named EXPLICITLY, not by a blanket
# `tests/*/` rule, so that a FORK's own target folders (tests/<your-app>/) commit
# normally. In your own fork, delete these lines.
/tests/abv-bg/
/tests/helpers/
config/pipeline.config.demo-abv-bg.json
